Section 325 of the Indian Penal Code (45 of 186 0), provides that whoever, 
except in the case provided for by section 335, vol untarily causes grievous hurt, 
shall be subject to certain punishments. A is charged with voluntarily causing grievous hurt  under section 325.   The burden of proving the circumstances bringing th e case under section 335 lies  on A.

